prodNameC: 羅氏免疫分析肌鈣蛋白I檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL:Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL;preservative.
R1 Anti-cardiac troponin I-Ab-biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:2 biotinylated monoclonal anti-cardiac troponin I-antibodies(mouse) 0.8 mg/L each; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L,pH 7.4; preservative; inhibitors.
R2 Anti-cardiac troponin I-Ab-~Ru(bpy)2+3(black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL: 2 monoclonal anti-cardiac troponin I-antibodies (mouse) labeled with ruthenium complex 0.8
mg/L and 0.005 mgl/L respectively; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 7.4;preservative;inhibitors.

(CalSet)
Reagents - working solutions
TN-I Call: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
TN-I Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Troponin I (recombinant, human) in two concentration ranges (approx. 0.4 Mg/L or ng/mL and approx. 30 Mg/L or ng/mL) in a human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 在體外以免疫分析法定量測定人類血清和血漿中的心肌肌鈣蛋白I(cardiac troponin I)。
